## Authentication

At the ARXivar API URL: **NomeServer/ARXivarNextAuthentication** open the "Software" menu link:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000473-0/21DoCSolutionsForArxivarNext.png"><br>

Press "+" and enter the Client ID

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000473-0/19DoCSolutionsForArxivarNext.png"><br>

Select "Activate". Now on the list you can see the Client ID and the relative Secret

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000473-0/20DoCSolutionsForArxivarNext.png"><br>